title: Invisible, Inc. (Incognita) v03.09.2014
description:
From Klei Entertainment, the creators of Don't Starve and Mark of the Ninja
Invisible, Inc. (previously known as Incognita)

"Invisible, Inc. is a mercenary espionage agency operating in the late 21st century. Infiltrate procedurally generated corporate facilities in tense, turn-based missions where every move could be your last. Find profit in chaos as you guide your team around the world in search of lucrative contracts."

v03.09.2014 changelog:
New Features:
- 1 new program, item and daemon (go find them!)
Difficulty settings:
- Easy
-- Safes, guards, and rewards are more lucrative.
-- Alarm stages ramp less quickly.
-- Neural Disrupters knock out for longer
- Normal
-- Safes, guards and rewards are less lucrative.
-- More firewalls protect the mainframe.
Bug fixes:
- Bioshot recharges properly
- Dropping body bug fix.
- Artifacts give proper rewards.
- Tool tips clean up.
- Myriad of small bug fixes
